<div class="answer-head">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730"
class="zm-item-link-avatar"
href="/people/kaiserwang730">
<img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/21cb65b48_s.jpg"
class="zm-list-avatar"
data-source="//pic1.zhimg.com/21cb65b48_s.jpg" />
</a>



<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730" href="/people/kaiserwang730">Kaiser</a>，<strong title="天亮了" class="zu-question-my-bio">天亮了</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="323">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$k-klevin" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/k-klevin" class="zg-link" title="K KLevin">K KLevin</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$aaa-ssss-88" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/aaa-ssss-88" class="zg-link" title="AAA Ssss">AAA Ssss</a>、</span><span class="user-block">知乎用户</span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="4170682" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix">《水浒传》<br><br><blockquote>真人答道：“此乃是前代老祖天师锁镇魔王之殿。”太尉又问道：“如何上面重重叠叠贴着许多封皮？”真人答道：“此是老祖<b>大唐</b>洞玄国师封锁魔王在此。但是经传一代天师，亲手便添一道封皮，使其子子孙孙，不得妄开。走了魔君，非常利害。”</blockquote><br><blockquote>话说当时住持真人对洪太尉说道：“太尉不知，此殿中当初是祖老天师洞玄真人传下法符，嘱付道：‘此殿内镇锁着三十六员天罡星，七十二座地煞星，共是一百单八个魔君在里面。”<br></blockquote><br>所以一百零八将其实是唐朝被封印在电饭锅里的一百零八个魔君集体穿越而来。<br>如果书成于当代，名字或许应该叫：<br><br>《重生之霸道哥哥爱上我》


</div>

</div>
